med from one of the worlds largest merge key challenges compliance settlement a unit of citigroup will pay  million to settle civil charges alleging it failed to enforce policies designed to prevent and detect insider trading us regulators said according to an biographical highlights born circa  in taiwan hu earned bachelor of science and master of science degrees in electrical engineering and computer science with a concentration in economics from the massachusetts institute of technology these companies are using boardroom insiders to close bigger deals faster view full samples now watch our video   boardroom insiders inc all rights reserved all trademarks are the property of their respective owners privacy policy contact us hu w bradford top holdings whalewisdom search all search f filers only search sec filer search stocks only search mgmt inv cos only etfs only search active hu w bradford • new york ny how do i update this listing hu w bradford is based out of new york summary dg insider form  create email alert × email notification log in or signup to see more advanced email alert options such as selecting any type of sec form multiple filers or classes of filers and much more or to simply have an email sent to you whenever we receive a new f filing from hu w bradford enter your email address below and choose submit your email cancel contact info hu w bradford  lexington avenue th fl new york ny     recent sec filings  filed on   filed on   filed on   filed on   filed on   filed on   filed on   filed on   filed on   filed on  schedule d and g events since  subscription required form   nonderivative insider transactions since  loading elevate your investments try it for free